  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Saving Gap Evaluation Results</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loiodbfdc5536a51204be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Saving Gap Evaluation Results </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n\n<p class=\"p\"> When you run ALM simulation, you have the option of saving the results from gap\nevaluations. You can then display the saved results at a later point in time. </p>\n<p class=\"p\"> You can use a report to update gap evaluation results that have already been saved. This\nis useful from a performance point of view if only one or a few portfolio hierarchy nodes\nhave been affected by changes. </p>\n<p class=\"p\"> If you no longer require the gap results you saved, you can delete them using a report.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Activities\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Activities</h2>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Saving gap results</span>\n</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Start the ALM simulation. For general information about using ALM simulation see\n<a class=\"xref\" href=\"cffdc5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Executing\nAnalysis/Simulation</a> . </p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Processing</span> tab page. </p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Enter the value 1 or 2 in the field <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Processing Mode.</span>\n</p><p class=\"p\"> 1 = Calculate, save and display results </p><p class=\"p\"> 2 = Calculate and save results </p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Enter a short description. The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Save ID</span> is assigned\nautomatically by the system when the gap results are saved. </p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio2588c753b1081d4be10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span> . </p><aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<p class=\"p\"> You can display the saved results by choosing processing mode 3 <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Display\nsaved results.</span> Then enter the save ID in the relevant field. If you do\nnot know the save ID, you can search for it using the short description. </p></aside></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Updating gap results</span>\n</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">In the SAP Easy Access screen, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Accounting</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Financial Supply Chain Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Market Risk Analyzer</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Asset/Liability Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tools</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Gap Results</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Update Results of Gap Analysis</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Enter the old save ID, under which the results were saved, for the results you want\nto update.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Fill the fields <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Portfolio\nHierarchy</span>.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Now choose the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Portfolio Hierarchy Node</span> for which you want to\nupdate the gap results.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Enter a short description ( <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">New Text for Saved Results</span>\nfield).</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio2588c753b1081d4be10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span>.</p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Deleting gap results</span></p>\n<ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">In the SAP Easy Access screen, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Accounting</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Financial Supply Chain Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Market Risk Analyzer</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Asset/Liability Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tools</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Gap Results</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete Results of Gap Analysis</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose the save ID under which the data was saved that you want to delete.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio2588c753b1081d4be10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span>.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Check the log.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loiofcbbc7531dc61d4be10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Back</span>.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Set the indicator <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Update Run</span>.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio2588c753b1081d4be10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span>.</p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Displaying the saved gap results (header information)</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can display the header information of saved gap results. In the SAP Easy Access\nscreen, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Accounting</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Financial Supply Chain Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Market Risk Analyzer</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Asset/Liability Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tools</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Gap Results</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Display Results of Gap Analysis (Header Information)</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>. You will then see the following information:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper tablenoborder\"><table summary=\"\" class=\"table\" frame=\"border\" border=\"1\" rules=\"all\"><colgroup><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"><col width=\"7.6923076923076925%\"></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e455\"><p class=\"p\"> SaveID </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e461\"><p class=\"p\"> Short name </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e467\"><p class=\"p\"> View </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e473\"><p class=\"p\"> PF hier. </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e479\"><p class=\"p\"> PH node </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e486\"><p class=\"p\"> Evaldate </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e492\"><p class=\"p\"> Eval </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e498\"><p class=\"p\"> Gap type </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e504\"><p class=\"p\"> Old ID </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e510\"><p class=\"p\"> Updated </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e516\"><p class=\"p\"> Entered by </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e523\"><p class=\"p\"> Entry on (date) </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e529\"><p class=\"p\"> Entry at (time) </p></th>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e538\"><p class=\"p\"> 1 </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e544\"><p class=\"p\"> Europe </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e550\"><p class=\"p\"> 001 </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e556\"><p class=\"p\"> 202 </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e562\"><p class=\"p\"> 1 </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e569\"><p class=\"p\"> 10/01/00 </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e575\"><p class=\"p\"> 500 </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e581\"><p class=\"p\"> 500 </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e587\"><p class=\"p\"> 0 </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e593\"><p class=\"p\"> </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e599\"><p class=\"p\"> Smith </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e606\"><p class=\"p\"> 10/01/00 </p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d187258e612\"><p class=\"p\"> 12:54:30 </p></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e455 d187258e538 \"><p class=\"p\"> 2 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e461 d187258e544 \"><p class=\"p\"> Fixed-term deposit EUR </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e467 d187258e550 \"><p class=\"p\"> 001 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e473 d187258e556 \"><p class=\"p\"> 202 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e479 d187258e562 \"><p class=\"p\"> 63 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e486 d187258e569 \"><p class=\"p\"> 10/01/00 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e492 d187258e575 \"><p class=\"p\"> 500 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e498 d187258e581 \"><p class=\"p\"> 500 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e504 d187258e587 \"><p class=\"p\"> 1 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e510 d187258e593 \"><p class=\"p\"> </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e516 d187258e599 \"><p class=\"p\"> Smith </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e523 d187258e606 \"><p class=\"p\"> 10/15/00 </p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d187258e529 d187258e612 \"><p class=\"p\"> 14:35:35 </p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n1t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n1t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Header information for deleted gaps results is no longer shown when saved gap results\nare displayed.</p></aside>\n</div>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
